Freedom of the Press Foundation (FPF) maintains custom-compiled Linux
kernel images for use in SecureDrop and SecureDrop Workstation.
The kernel source has been patched with the grsecurity modifications,
and only binaries are available in the FPF apt repository.

Under the terms of the GPL, any user in possession of this offer has a right
to request the source code used to compile those binaries.
You may submit a written request to:

    Freedom of the Press Foundation
    49 Flatbush Ave, #1017
    Brooklyn, NY 11217

Or via email to:

    source-offer@freedom.press

A full copy of this message can be found online at
https://github.com/freedomofpress/securedrop-workstation/blob/main/SOURCE_OFFER
